
'''Francine Munyaneza''' ni umucuruzikazi n'umushabitsi w'umunyarwandakazi, washinze kandi akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru wa Munyax Eco Ltd, isosiyete ikora ingufu zituruka ku mirasire y'izuba ikora kuva mu 2013 kandi ikorera i [[Kigali]]. Niwe washinze kandi akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru wa La Maison Verte, umushinga wo kubaka ubusugire bw'ibidukikije. <ref name=":1">https://www.afdb.org/en/news-keywords/global-gender-summit-2019</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Munyaneza yari yarigishijwe imari n'imicungire y'ubucuruzi mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] kaminuza yitwa Université Catholique de Louvain. <ref name=":1">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.afdb.org/en/news-keywords/global-gender-summit-2019 "Global Gender Summit 2019"]. ''African Development Bank - Building today, a better Africa tomorrow''<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2021-11-25</span></span>.</cite></ref>

== Umwuga ==
Usibye impamyabumenyi ye, Munyaneza yahisemo gusubira mu rugo (mu [[Rwanda]]) kugira ngo atangire ubucuruzi bwe bw’ingufu zishobora kuvugururwa kandi buhendutse kugira ngo akemure ibibazo by’amashanyarazi mu cyaro ndetse n’amazi ashyushye mu mijyi myinshi yo mu [[Rwanda]] . <ref>https://www.greengrowthknowledge.org/person/francine-munyaneza</ref> Ibyo byabaye nyuma yimyaka 20 yuburambe mu burasirazuba bwo hagati, [[Burayi|Uburayi]], [[Afurika]], [[Aziya]] na [[Amerika]] akora ku nzego nkuru z'ubuyobozi hamwe n’amasosiyete akomeye yo muri [[Amerika]] yo mu majyaruguru, ndetse n’imiryango iharanira ubutabazi ya Komite mpuzamahanga ya Croix-Rouge (ICRC), Médecins Sans Frontières or Doctors Without Borders(MSF. <ref name=":0">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/lifestyle/how-one-woman-leveraging-renewable-energy-lift-other-women</ref> Munyaneza yagaragaje ubusobanuro bw'ingufu z'izuba mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref>https://www.cnbcafrica.com/2021/how-rwanda-can-tap-into-the-potential-of-solar-power/</ref> [[Rwanda]] ni igihugu kiri kuzamuka mubijyanye n'uburinganire , <ref>https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2018/01/10/577018509/rwanda-ranks-in-the-top-5-for-gender-equity-do-its-teen-girls-agree</ref> <ref>https://www3.weforum.org/docs/WEF_GGGR_2017.pdf</ref> Munyaneza yaharaniye kuzamura ubushobozi bw'igitsinagore, <ref>https://www.energy.gov/articles/womens-clean-energy-wednesday-spotlight-rwanda</ref> kandi azwiho guha umwanya bagenzibe b'igitsinagore haba mu kazi ko gucuruza ndetse no mukubungabuka ihindagurika ry'ikirere . <ref>https://alurb.org/index.php/personnel/francine-munyaneza/</ref> <ref>https://www.epdrwanda.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Quarter3.pdf</ref> Kuva mu 2014, isosiyete ye Munyax Eco yatoranijwe na REG ( Rwanda Energy Group, isosiyete ikora amashanyarazi mu gihugu) kugira ngo itange  ingufu za Solar Water Heaters. Niyo mpamvu isosiyete ye yagiye ikurikirana sisitemu zirenga 800 za Solar Water Heating sisitemu kubakiriya barenga 1200 B2B & B2C itanga ingufu kubantu barenga 10,000, inatanga amashanyarazi yizuba kuri sisitemu ya gride, Solar Street itara nibindi bikoresho byizuba (Solar Home Systems, Solar Cold Chain and other Solar productive use equipment). <ref>https://www.socialopencamp.org/munyax-eco-rwanda/?lang=en</ref> Nyuma y’imyaka itanu ikora, Munyax Eco yamenyekanye n’itsinda ry’imigabane rya Londres ko iri mu "ma business yihuta cyane muri [[Afurika]] " muri raporo iheruka gukorwa na "Companies to Inspire Africa", yashyizwe ahagaragara muri Mutarama 2019. <ref name=":0" /> Munyaneza na ICU basinyanye amasezerano yo gutanga ibikoresho byubwubatsi bwa sisitemu yo gufotora mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]] mu rwego rwo kuzamura umusaruro w’amashanyarazi hifashishijwe imirasire ishobora kongera ingufu muri [[Afurika]]. <ref>https://www.icu.it/en/icu-signed-the-contract-for-the-supply-of-construction-equipment-of-a-photovoltaic-system-in-burundi/</ref> Munyaneza yigaragaje cyane akarere k'ibiyaga bigari hamwe n’ubucuruzi bwe bushya bw’ingufu zishobora kubaho binyuze mu ngorane zo kubona inguzanyo. <ref>https://www.euronews.com/next/2014/04/02/europe-and-africa-working-together-to-build-investment-opportunities</ref>

== Ibyagezweho n'ibihembo ==
Francine Munyaneza yatowe vuba aha muri AFSIA Solar Awards 2021 n’ishyirahamwe ry’imirasire y’izuba muri [[Afurika]] kandi yegukana igihembo cyitwa “The Residential Project of the year” kubera ibikorwa by’ubushyuhe bw’izuba mu gihugu hose. <ref>http://afsiasolar.com/nominees-for-the-afsia-solar-awards-2021-are-announced/</ref> Yatowe nkumukinnyi wumwaka urenga 30, abahatanira Founder of The Year Awards 2020  - muri Afrika yuburasirazuba . <ref>https://foya.thefounder.africa/post/finalist-nominees-for-founder-of-the-year-awards-2020-east-africa-founder-of-the-year-over-30</ref> Munyaneza yakiriye inkunga muri ARIE 2021 binyuze muri USADF ( Fondasiyo ya Amerika ishinzwe iterambere ). <ref>https://www.usadf.gov/press-release/815</ref>

